Sentencas: BaZr0.9Y0.1O3-delta (BZY):BaCe0.86Y0.1Zn0.04O3-delta (BCYZn) proton conductors were synthesized by a gel polymerization and ball milling method.
Titulo: Synthesis, microstructure and electrical properties of BaZr0.9Y0.1O3-δ:BaCe0.86Y0.1Zn0.04O3-δ proton conductors

Sentencas: XRD results show that the phases of Y doped BaZrO3 and Y and Zn co-doped BaCeO3 were identified for the composite electrolytes calcined at 1000 degrees C for 3 h. After sintering at 1350 degrees C for 5 h, only one phase is observed by XRD, which suggests the formation of BaZrO3-BaCeO3 solid solution.
Titulo: Synthesis, microstructure and electrical properties of BaZr0.9Y0.1O3-δ:BaCe0.86Y0.1Zn0.04O3-δ proton conductors

Sentencas: The relative density and conductivity of samples increase with increasing BCYZn content.
Titulo: Synthesis, microstructure and electrical properties of BaZr0.9Y0.1O3-δ:BaCe0.86Y0.1Zn0.04O3-δ proton conductors

Sentencas: The total conductivity reaches 7.4 x 10(-3) S cm(-1) at 600 degrees C under moist Ar, and it can be used as a proton-conducting electrolyte for the intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Synthesis, microstructure and electrical properties of BaZr0.9Y0.1O3-δ:BaCe0.86Y0.1Zn0.04O3-δ proton conductors
